FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1774944309
OL,3,CMan who threatened petrol station
OL,4,Cworkers with imitation firearm jailed
OL,6,FPolice say one of the victims was able
OL,7,Fto flee the store and called Kent
OL,8,FPolice while Pollock climbed behind
OL,9,Fthe counter and forced open the till,
OL,10,Fstealing a quantity of cash.
OL,12,FA second victim managed to grab the
OL,13,Ffirearm and discovered it was a dummy.
OL,14,FHe threw it towards Pollock as he ran
OL,15,Ffrom the store.
OL,17,FThe victims chased Pollock outside and
OL,18,Fwere able to recover a small amount of
OL,19,Fmoney during the struggle.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
