OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1774944309
OL,3,CMan who threatened petrol station
OL,4,Cworkers with imitation firearm jailed
OL,6,FAn hour after the robbery, officers
OL,7,Fattended Pollock's home address in
OL,8,FBlossom Street and arrested him.
OL,10,FHe was charged with robbery, and
OL,11,Fpossession of an imitation firearm
OL,12,Fwith intent to cause fear of violence.
OL,14,FHe pleaded guilty to the offences at
OL,15,Fan earlier hearing and at Maidstone
OL,16,FCrown Court on Wednesday 25 March and
OL,17,Fwas jailed for six years and two
OL,18,Fmonths.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
