PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1774944309
OL,3,CMan who threatened petrol station
OL,4,Cworkers with imitation firearm jailed
OL,6,FInvestigating officer Detective
OL,7,FConstable Jack Seager said: "Pollock
OL,8,Fwas motivated by his own greed and
OL,9,Fused a weapon in a public place to
OL,10,Finflict fear towards the victims, not
OL,11,Fcaring about the long lasting impact
OL,12,Fhis actions could cause.
OL,14,F"Quick work by officers meant this
OL,15,Fdangerous individual has been taken
OL,16,Foff the streets and will spend a
OL,17,Fsignificant time behind bars."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
